Loan Application System
This project is a loan application system developed using HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, and JavaScript. It consists of several pages including a login page, KYC (Know Your Customer) page, basic details page, and final loan approval page.

Pages
Login Page

Allows users to log in using their credentials.
Validates user input using JavaScript for basic validation.
KYC Page

Collects and verifies user's identity information.
Includes form validation to ensure all required fields are filled.
Basic Details Page

Gathers additional personal and financial details required for the loan application.
Implements dynamic form elements using JavaScript for a user-friendly experience.
Final Loan Approval Page

Displays the status of the loan application (approved or rejected).
Provides a summary of the application details.
Technologies Used
HTML5
CSS3
Bootstrap 5
JavaScript (ES6)
Features
Responsive design using Bootstrap for mobile and desktop views.
Client-side form validation to ensure data integrity.
Interactive elements for an enhanced user experience.
Seamless navigation between pages using JavaScript.
Usage
To run the application locally:

Clone this repository:

bash
Copy code
git clone https://github.com/SwamyPonnameni/loan-application.git
Navigate to the project directory:

bash
Copy code
cd loan-application
Open index.html in your preferred web browser.


